555
01:04:04,612 --> 01:04:06,190
Elle change ?

556
01:04:07,490 --> 01:04:08,439
Pardon ?

557
01:04:09,242 --> 01:04:11,649
Votre fille
est en train de changer ?

558
01:04:14,205 --> 01:04:15,201
Je...

559
01:04:16,624 --> 01:04:18,416
